  <p class="sub">All four paths end with an extended carbon-cycle model + a 3-sentence attribution claim.</p>
  <div class="choice-intro">
    <strong>Learning Intention:</strong> I can describe the major anthropogenic carbon sources and rank them by scale, interpret the Keeling curve and 1850-present temperature record, and explain why attribution to greenhouse forcing rules out solar and volcanic explanations.
